data.title: Top 30+ Family Photographers in Italy
data.meta_description: Best family photographers in Florence, Rome, Venice, Catania, Perugia, Catanzaro, Reggio Calabria, Siena, Bologna, Fiumicino and all other cities in Italy with portfolios and prices for a photo shoot.
data.text:
Photography is my language and my pictures are my best way to express what I have to say. I love my job and I’m looking for the semplicity and feeling spontaneity, to give back a true story of an unforgettable day

I am based between Etna volcano and the sea, my greatest passion is to travel. I am a chronic observer and I photograph in an instinctive way. I love telling the tales of the people I meet trying to create a relationship based on empathy and trust. I adore my cats, art, cinema,books and flea markets

In every picture there is a bit of me, they tell a lot more things than I can describe with words. In ogni foto c'è un po' di me, esse raccontano molte più cose di quante io ne possa descrivere con le parole.

Today's moments ... are tomorrow's memories... Photography is a splendid language to tell stories, of ordinary people, of feelings, of ties. Wedding photography is this for me, to tell the emotions of a special day with images while maintaining the naturalness of the moments.

Venice's timeless beauty inspired my journey as a photographer. Specializing in weddings, surprise proposals, love stories, and individual portraits, I capture the essence of love in this enchanting city.

Wedding photographer based in Bologna and Elba Island. I am willing to join you wherever you decide to get married. I take real and honest photos, exactly as they appear before my eyes, to tell your story in the most truthful and spontaneous way possible.

Photography is not only something aesthetically beautiful, it is the perfect preservation of a memory, it is a witness, and it is also an instrument of dreams and imagination.

Hello, I am Marco Cammertoni, a WEDDING PHOTOGRAPHER based in UMBRIA, TOSCANA and COSTIERA AMALFITANA…. land where I was born. I love telling your LOVE STORIES with a REPORTAGE photo… capturing in every shot SIMPLE MOMENTS, EMOTIONS and MEMORIES that will remain forever alive…

My goal is to leave families a visual testimony of the commitment and patience in raising their children, their love, the full moments they have lived together. I would like to tell their stories in an honest and authentic way.

I was lucky enough to be able to photograph people all over the world and each of them has enriched me with their story. I like being able to tell stories through my images, enter the scene and live as it happens!

I am passioned about people and cultures, about the difference they make. My work enables me to be a part of this and where ever you are - I may follow you, to freeze the most wonderful moments of your time.
